      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数结束五日跌势，美国国债收益率上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国国债停止抛售，导致 10 年期国债收益率接近 4.5%，股市上涨，交易员密切关注当选总统唐纳德·特朗普政府的新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/asian-stocks-eye-soft-start-as-fed-doubts-simmer-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 22:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
